@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bwbune(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.36 - v0 + 0.21)) + wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.96)))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.17) + (v1 + 0.05 / v2 + 0.99)) + wp.abs(v2))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.78 * tmp + 0.31) / (tmp + 0.17 * v2 + 0.81)))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.64)
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
